Germany’s Ramsauer Says Road Repairs Call for Tolls, ARD Reports

-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   V i t s
-- 
2011-10-02T19:42:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-02/germany-s-ramsauer-says-road-repairs-call-for-tolls-ard-reports.html
German Transport Minister Peter Ramsauer said tolls are needed to finance repairs to the
country’s road network,  ARD television  reported, citing an
interview.  Ramsauer said the CSU, the Bavarian sister party of
 Chancellor Angela Merkel ’s Christian Democrats, will demand a
road toll at its next party convention.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christian Vits in Frankfurt at +49-69-92041-341 or
 cvits@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  